<br>
Cleared the courtyard with friends.<br>
<br>
Diamondskinned.<br>
<br>
I ran around to the ledge to the right of the zone exit..it hangs over the water.<br>
<br>
Lined up just in front of the door to the room, stood on the edge of the railing above the water staring at the wall.<br>
